pranks.punchlineText: You just locked it 5 seconds ago.

pranks.punchlineText: Delete them. You know which ones.

pranks.punchlineText: And you could have been working.

pranks.messageBody: Your thumb must be so strong.
pranks.punchlineText: From all that scrolling. Olympic level.

pranks.messageBody: I'm watching you type with one finger.

pranks.punchlineText: They said you'd regret this scroll session.

pranks.punchlineText: But I've seen you 47 times today.

Like a dog on a leash.

pranks.messageBody: Cast away from the power source.

pranks.punchlineText: 3 more percent and I would've been full!
I respect it. I do not respect it enough to stop.

pranks.messageBody: Time to pretend you can't hear people.
Headphones: the universal 'leave me alone' sign.

pranks.punchlineText: Let me guess: the same 5 songs on repeat?

pranks.messageBody: Back to disturbing everyone around you.
pranks.punchlineText: Play your music loud. Assert dominance.
Welcome back to reality, it's loud.

Either way, your music just blasted.

pranks.messageBody: Now everyone knows your music taste.
The outside world has been blocked.
Airplane mode: where your social anxiety goes to heal.

pranks.punchlineText: Except you're probably on a bus.
I operate on chaos waves. Still here.
Time to see what you missed: nothing.
Did you miss it? It missed you.
Your phone is happy. Are you?
Miss me while you were out?
Time to use all the data you don't have to.

pranks.messageBody: WiFi: the leash that brings you home.

pranks.punchlineText: Just like everyone else. Jk. Maybe.

pranks.punchlineText: Addiction is a strong word. But...

pranks.punchlineText: Oh wait, it's just you. You look tired.
